<paragraph blockId="13.[113,646,945,1035]" box="[113,181,945,971]" pageId="13" pageNumber="56">FERNS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="13.[113,646,945,1035]" pageId="13" pageNumber="56">Ferns, particularly marratialean tree ferns, are the most common element of the flora.</paragraph>
